{"tid":308224,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真係笑話]唔好笑你地認我做契爺","createTime":"2017-07-04T03:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T15:19:29.000Z","uid":30377,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"699534117039efc601e5705838201c17ffa5d91c","tid":308224,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"有一日 大波靚模Mandy岩岩出道 但佢好想快啲成名 於是佢就聽佢朋友介紹 去左搵一個好出名既睇相佬睇相...<br />\n<br />\nMandy:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    睇相佬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMandy: 呀睇相佬 我就靚模黎既 好想快啲出名 所以今次黎係想睇下....<br />\n<br />\n睇相佬： 屌你咪一輪咀咁講野先啦 你比我睇下你八字我先做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMandy: ok..等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後Mandy就開始寬衣解帶..<br />\n<br />\n睇相佬：呀靚模 請問你做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMandy: 你話要睇我八字呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇相佬：我係要睇你個八字 唔係要睇你對八字呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後Mandy就因為呢個post成左名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d4cc9a429647fbcf8f9dc1dc0f844a16bfd9fd","tid":308224,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aa15c5c4d7f95550443924e88783b156f5efea","tid":308224,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeecc2b6dda5f48a5455d11a0eb5378b85f2e6b8","tid":308224,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e189932f5625f07285bafd4b38219cb4521d899c","tid":308224,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:01:06.000Z"